WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.490
I think it's very important
to be extremely thoughtful

00:00:02.490 --> 00:00:06.390
about how does this new
technology affect all humans.

00:00:06.390 --> 00:00:08.970
Running a tech company
at a very high pace,

00:00:08.970 --> 00:00:11.550
it's not for the faint of heart.

00:00:11.550 --> 00:00:14.910
Doing it right and making
sure that even though it's.

00:00:14.910 --> 00:00:16.650
everyone has to move really, really fast,

00:00:16.650 --> 00:00:18.506
do so responsibly.

00:00:18.506 --> 00:00:21.173
(gentle music)

00:00:23.310 --> 00:00:26.400
Lovable lets anyone take
an idea for software

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:28.590
and build it themselves
by having a conversation

00:00:28.590 --> 00:00:29.553
with our platform.

00:00:30.540 --> 00:00:34.380
With the business of
unlocking new economies,

00:00:34.380 --> 00:00:36.180
empowering every human out there

00:00:36.180 --> 00:00:38.430
who wants to create something.

00:00:38.430 --> 00:00:39.990
- What is unlocked by Anthropic

00:00:39.990 --> 00:00:41.400
and Lovable working together?

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:43.950
- Since everything's been exploding,

00:00:43.950 --> 00:00:45.630
there's been more support

00:00:45.630 --> 00:00:47.160
and more interactions between our teams.

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:49.620
We've gotten dedicated people
from the Anthropic team

00:00:49.620 --> 00:00:50.453
that works with us.

00:00:50.453 --> 00:00:52.650
It starts feeling more like
we're building something

00:00:52.650 --> 00:00:56.043
together than just a
customer vendor relationship.

00:00:57.030 --> 00:01:00.210
We launched this product two months ago.

00:01:00.210 --> 00:01:03.150
User growth has been really good.

00:01:03.150 --> 00:01:07.050
Needless to say, I think we
are all standing in front

00:01:07.050 --> 00:01:08.370
of a generational shift.

00:01:08.370 --> 00:01:11.460
My advice to founders working
with Anthropic would be

00:01:11.460 --> 00:01:15.870
to dig into a partnership and ask for help

00:01:15.870 --> 00:01:17.070
and spend time with the team

00:01:17.070 --> 00:01:20.760
because these are humans
that actually really care.

00:01:20.760 --> 00:01:23.490
- So I've heard you say
the most underrated moat in

00:01:23.490 --> 00:01:24.720
AI is trust.

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:27.210
- Something that I
think is very rare in AI

00:01:27.210 --> 00:01:30.960
is a trusted brand that people
love and keep coming back to

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:33.295
and to have that trusted brand,

00:01:33.295 --> 00:01:36.990
that's not something that
you magically achieve.

00:01:36.990 --> 00:01:38.670
It's really warming my heart,

00:01:38.670 --> 00:01:41.308
feeling the exciting things
everyone is building.

00:01:41.308 --> 00:01:42.540
(audience applauds)

00:01:42.540 --> 00:01:47.400
One of the values we have at
Lovable is to care deeply,

00:01:47.400 --> 00:01:49.673
constantly be obsessed and think about

00:01:49.673 --> 00:01:52.770
what do our customers
need, what they want.

00:01:52.770 --> 00:01:56.730
It's about the craft and every
detail of what you're doing

00:01:56.730 --> 00:01:58.620
when you're improving
your product experience

00:01:58.620 --> 00:02:01.950
and making sure to make
this like super hard topic

00:02:01.950 --> 00:02:03.843
of software development simple.

00:02:05.250 --> 00:02:07.620
(speaking foreign language)

00:02:07.620 --> 00:02:09.000
- I'm super excited about this world

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:10.890
where more things are possible.

00:02:10.890 --> 00:02:15.840
There is fundamentally more
human agency that's unlocked

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:19.050
when frictions for starting a company

00:02:19.050 --> 00:02:22.440
and building your product,
they start disappearing.

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:25.650
So I think we're entering an era

00:02:25.650 --> 00:02:27.990
where there are more societal problems

00:02:27.990 --> 00:02:29.280
that are getting solved.

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:32.520
We're seeing that live
with millions of people

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:34.873
building on top of our platform.

00:02:34.873 --> 00:02:38.373
(gentle music continues)

